'''第二十一饕餮军团'''（{{lang-en|Legio XXI Rapax}}）<ref>Adkins,Lesley Adkins,Roy A.（1998）.''Handbook to Life in Ancient Rome''.Oxford University Press,USA.ISBN 9780195123326.</ref>[[古罗马|古罗马]][[军队|军队]]建制名称。由[[屋大维|屋大维]]于公元前31年建立并存在至公元92年。该军团曾先后参加{{tsl|en|Cantabrian Wars|坎塔布连战争}}<ref name="e"/>和镇压{{tsl|en|Rhaetian people|雷蒂安人}}起义等一系列相关军事活动。目前该军团的最终结局尚未定论。<ref>{{de}}{{Cite book |title=Legions and veterans: Roman army papers 1971–2000 (Mavors. Roman Army Researches Band 12) |author=Lawrence J. F. Keppie |publisher=Steiner |year=2000 |isbn=978-3-515-07744-6 |location=Stuttgart |pages=p 151}}</ref>普遍的观点认为，公元92年，该军团在[[多瑙河#下游段|多瑙河下游]]与[[萨尔马提亚人|萨尔马提亚人]]的战斗中全军覆没。<ref>{{de}}{{Cite book |title=''Geschichte der römischen Kaiserzeit'' |last=Christ |first=Karl |publisher=C. H. Beck Verlag |place=München |year=1995 |isbn=3-406-36316-4 |pages=p 274}}</ref>造成该军团覆灭的主力可能为萨尔马提亚中的[[罗克索拉尼人|罗克索拉尼]]部落。<ref>{{cite book|first=Julian |last=Bennett |title=''Trajan: Optimus Princeps: a Life and Times''|url=https://archive.org/details/trajanoptimuspri00benn |page=[https://archive.org/details/trajanoptimuspri00benn/page/33 33]|isbn=9780415165242|publisher=[[Routledge|Routledge]]|year=1997}}</ref>
